--------------------------> Important Topics -------------------------------------->
1. Ternary operator
2. Switch
3. Loops (Do-while, For, For each)
4. Using break & continue
5. Recursion
6. Random Numbers & Math class
7. Don’t Learn Syntax
8. toString Method
9. String class
10.StringBuffer vs StringBuilder
11. Final keyword

<---------------------------------Explaination---------------------------------------->

1. Ternary operator
-> isme kuch nhai shamj ne layak ye apne ko ata hi hai fhir bhi revise karne ke liye java notes
jake dhek shakta hai.

2. Switch
-> ye bhi apan ko ata hai to sirf hamare swithStatement wale class me jake ek bar revise kar shakte hai

3. Loops (Do-while, For, For each)
-> do - while loop ek barr to chalega hi bhale hi kuch bhi hojaye kyu ki condtion ham log bad me
lhikte hai .
-> for loop ye shab to ata hi hai
-> forEach bhai iska jake ek barr syntax dhek lena baku ye array ke liye bhot use hota hai.

4. Using break & continue
-> break keyword khai pe bhi ajaye to shamjana ki whia pe wo loop ya to conditional statement end
hora hai.
-> jaha pe continue lhika hai apn ne to continue kya karega wo firse condtion pe jake check karga
and agar condition true hoti hai to particular code ko wapis chala dega .
-> continue skip kardega ek iteration ko kyu ki jaise condition match hoti hai to wo shabse phele i++
pr jata hai and bolta hai ki i ko update karo.

5. Recursion
-> Recursion ka matlab ek aisa function jo apne ko hi call kar raha ho use bolte hai ham recursion .
-> Recursion isme ham apne hi function ko chota karke call karte rhete hai jab tak ham apne base
tak na phoch jaye agar hamne apna base case nhai diya to infinite chalta rhaega and system crash
 hojayega.
-> isko ek barr dehklena kasie hora hai .
-> isko tabhi use karte hai jab problem choti hoti jati hai and apne base case tak phauch ke band hojaye.

6. Random Numbers & Math class
-> ye wala topic apne KGMath wale me practice kiya hai whai se jake dhek le.

7. Don’t Learn Syntax
->Syntax ko yaad maat karo concept ko shamjo.

8. toString Method or 9.string class
-> toString() ye method har calss me automatic ata hai har object ka ek unique has code hota hai
or ye toString method whai hascode return karta hai out put me .
-> isme ham object ka description show karte hai .
-> string wale object store hote to heap me hi hai lekin special jagaha pe jiska name string pool
hota hai .
-> agar me new ke shaat string banaunga to wo store ko heap me and normal string banaunga to wo
store hoga string pool me jo ki heap ke and ek khali space hota hai.
-> string ya kisi bhi object ki value ko compare karne ke liye hamesa equals()  ye wala
method use hota hai.
-> array ke andar jo ham .lenght lagate hai usko ham ek field bolte hai
-> string ke andar jo ham .length() lagate hai usko ham bolte hai method.

10.StringBuffer vs StringBuilder
->stringBuilder ka use ham .append method ko chalane ke liye karte hai
-> jab bhi hum stringBuilder ko use karenge to particular string mutable hojayegi isliye wo heap me
store hogi na hi string pool
->stringBuilder and stringBuffer me ek hi diffrence wo hai ki single threaeded me stringBuilder
jyada acha perform karta hai or stringBuffer multithreaded me acha perform karta hai .

11. Final keyword
-> Final keyword ham log jaha bhi laga denge uski value final hoajayegi matalab uski value ko koi
change nhai kar shakta
->final variable ko hame turant value deni padti hai kyu wo change nhai hoga and reassign bhi nhai
hoga .
-> final variable ko ham hamesa SNAKE_CASE me lhikenge kyu turant pata chal jaye ki ye variable
mera final hai or iski value bhi hai.